# Plan Enforcer runtime artifacts - ephemeral state, not project memory.
# (We do NOT blanket-ignore .plan-enforcer/ so durable files like
# awareness.md and archive/ stay tracked. Add new ephemera here.)
.plan-enforcer/.*
.plan-enforcer/ledger.md
.plan-enforcer/config.md
.plan-enforcer/combobulate.md
.plan-enforcer/research.md
.plan-enforcer/discuss.md
.plan-enforcer/checks/
.plan-enforcer/statusline-state.json
node_modules/
*.log
.claude/
benchmarks/results/
benchmarks/framework-comparison/results/
